0:00:00.000,0:00:05.500
Man of God, please help me! I was shot by an armed robber.

0:00:05.500,0:00:09.520
Prophet T.B. Joshua prays for this man in the power of the Holy Ghost

0:00:09.520,0:00:13.160
and uproots whatever that is not of Jesus Christ in his life.

0:00:13.160,0:00:15.460
Glory be to God! He is free.

